<?php
 namespace Compassplus\Sdk; class Service extends \Sabre\Xml\Service { public function write($rootElementName, $value, $contextUri = null) { $w = $this->getWriter(); $w->openMemory(); $w->contextUri = $contextUri; $w->setIndent(true); $w->startDocument('1.0', 'UTF-8'); $w->writeElement($rootElementName, $value); return $w->outputMemory(); } } 